{"tid":1374432,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界聽日同我出遮打然後順手買雞蛋番屋企","createTime":"2019-07-27T18:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T05:19:18.000Z","uid":283049,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"64dcb0e7b97e0c89ff3760635eabe016eb480d96","tid":1374432,"uid":283049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:42:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雞蛋係時候要進化變成臭雞蛋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔知有無前線巴絲打已經用緊，但臭雞蛋保留咗雞蛋本身易攜帶、具侮辱性嘅特質外，更強化咗氣味上嘅攻勢。我聞過，真係臭到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於考慮會否TK，首先雞蛋可以遠程，手足們最近都用開都差唔多上曬手幾神準。此外都係個味道TK，聞到係難頂但起碼唔會對身體造成嚴重損傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無仔細研究過，但買番嚟擺喺太陽下曬足2日我估點都會壞</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但記得mark番清楚邊啲係壞蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔小心拎番屋企煮嚟食就仆街了</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外，我見好似無乜人討論黑警最近幾次用多咗強光照射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">喺強光照射下，人係會不自覺地唔敢有大動作</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家可以效法一下，去五金舖買啲勁嘅電筒，入夜後照實班黑警，等記者影得清楚佢地、手足睇得清楚情況之餘，俾足夠嘅心理壓力佢地</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">臭雞蛋同強光照射，都係侮辱佢地同俾心理壓力，雖然鬥武力可能贏唔過班有槍嘅仆街，但咁樣起碼可以俾到少少壓力對面</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命，明天遮打花園見</span></span>"},{"pid":"ecbb2b7a9e25b5d7b3f8c4c464f192de6b800cd7","tid":1374432,"uid":283049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:44:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自推，有無手足知邊度有得賣強力電筒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"c4662daf84887ff6924a35a17b57cda55a38022e","tid":1374432,"uid":283049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推"},{"pid":"56ee00a6210a9ef53fed1a6ad8702a4998604eb9","tid":1374432,"uid":65186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ecbb2b7a9e25b5d7b3f8c4c464f192de6b800cd7","tid":1374432,"uid":283049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:44:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自推，有無手足知邊度有得賣強力電筒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:11:49.000Z","msg":"鴨記<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea79c2408456267e10190dc67b246a8329fd348","tid":1374432,"uid":128388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:23:19.000Z","msg":"今日請每人帶自己gear, 雞蛋,番茄,橙,蕉等等"},{"pid":"d3b184b73dbeef3c10b88fc65baa2e069b4058b2","tid":1374432,"uid":128388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:23:32.000Z","msg":"今日請每人帶自己gear, 雞蛋,番茄,橙,蕉等等"},{"pid":"dadeff576bb514b8f7d8a1c77bc498c2f9fc0d8d","tid":1374432,"uid":283049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:50:17.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3def347e46157ce88fdb32288fe4246533d31db7","tid":1374432,"uid":283049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cwjC7yr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcwjC7yr.png&h=aa8ded4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一陣見<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"